high_descs: Turn around and walk toward the toilet.
Grab the potato from the tank of the toilet.
Turn around to the right and carry the potato to the sink.
Put the potato in the sink, fill the sink with water, drain the sink and remove the potato.
Hold the potato close to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Take the potato off of the back of the toilet and wash it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the toilet.
Take the potato from the toilet.
Turn around and go near the sink.
Placed the potato into the sink and washed it.
Then take and place the potato on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Washed and placed the potato on the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the toilet.
Pick the potato from the toilet.
Turn right and walk towards the sink.
Put the potato in the sink, rinse it off, and pick it back up.
Place the Potato near the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the Potato near the sink.
